Make perfect Pumpkin Spice Lattes with Pumpkin Spice Oat Barista Blend. Steam it, froth it and add it to your espresso. That’s it! It’s a one-stop-shop to make your favorite festive latte at home. Completely dairy-free and still deliciously creamy, every sip delivers the fall flavors of real pumpkin puree and warm spices. Made from simple, plant-based ingredients, with no nuts, soy, gluten or carrageenan, it strikes the perfect balance between sweet pumpkin, spicy notes of cinnamon, nutmeg, and ginger, and the natural creaminess of North American-grown gluten-free oats.  

Califia Farms Pumpkin Spice Oat Barista Blend is made with plant-based, dairy-free ingredients that are Non-GMO Certified, Kosher, vegan, and free from carrageenan.

name: Milkadamia Barista Macadamia Milk 32oz
description:
Milkadamia Latte Da Macadamia Nut Milk is the butteriest and most butterful of the nut milks. It’s made from sustainably grown Macadamia nuts, one of the few Aussie exports that doesn't sport a pouch. But these toughest of nuts make the creamiest of milks, milk that imparts a richness to your beverages without muting your daily grind’s heady flavors.  
  
Milkadamia's family farm is renowned for their restorative and regenerative approach to farming. By planting thousands of trees Each year, Milkadamia helps reforest areas that have been deforested for dairy farming.
